channel.title: Comments on: Stream: The Dirty Projectors “Stillness Is the Move”

item.title: By: Logan Young
item.dc:creator: Logan Young
item.description: I was late to the whole DP party, but I totally agree - Coffman's voice is out of this world. Don't know if it's a misprint or not, but they're opening up for TVOtR (ugh!) in Charlotte at Amos' Southend Thursday, July 11th.
item.content:encoded: I was late to the whole DP party, but I totally agree – Coffman’s voice is out of this world. Don’t know if it’s a misprint or not, but they’re opening up for TVOtR (ugh!) in Charlotte at Amos’ Southend Thursday, July 11th.
